# ComfyUI photoreal pipeline — generated output and proprietary game assets.
# gallery.html (the viewer) IS committed; all binary output is not.
creative_suite/comfy/photoreal/assets/          # pak00 PNGs extracted from Steam (986 MB, proprietary)
creative_suite/comfy/photoreal/pipelines/       # full_overnight.py batch output (large, regenerable)
creative_suite/comfy/photoreal/pass1/           # legacy first-pass output
creative_suite/comfy/photoreal/e2e/             # generated E2E test images (regenerable)
creative_suite/comfy/photoreal/assets.db        # runtime SQLite DB (regenerable)
creative_suite/comfy/photoreal/run.log
creative_suite/comfy/photoreal/run_err.log
# gallery.html IS tracked — it is the visual viewer, not generated output
!creative_suite/comfy/photoreal/gallery.html
creative_suite/comfy/photoreal/compare/         # old comparison UI

